=== 拍攝 ===
主要拍攝於2014年2月10日至5月14日於[[多倫多|多倫多]]{{tsl|en|Pinewood Toronto Studios|松林多倫多工作室}}（Pinewood Toronto Studios）進行<ref>{{cite web|author1=Tom Hiddleston|title=And That. Is A Wrap. On Crimson Peak.|url=https://twitter.com/twhiddleston/status/467560118104494080|publisher=Tom Hiddleston Verified Twitter|accessdate=2014-06-18|date=2014-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715024919/https://twitter.com/twhiddleston/status/467560118104494080|archive-date=2014-07-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在4月28日，於[[安大略省|安大略省]]的漢密爾頓開始於皇后街南、主街及國王街取景拍攝。這段期間，道路和交通都被封閉，並搭建了哥德式的建築外觀，那哥德式外觀的蘇格蘭教派建設之西翼有突出的部分<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/guillermo-del-toros-crimson-peak-renamed-haunted-peak-will-spookily-materialize-in-theaters-april-2015-20131025|publisher=IndieWire|title=Updated: Guillermo Del Toro's 'Crimson Peak' Will Spookily Materialize In Theaters April 2015|date=2013-10-25|last=Taylor|first=Drew|7=|access-date=2015-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110222728/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/guillermo-del-toros-crimson-peak-renamed-haunted-peak-will-spookily-materialize-in-theaters-april-2015-20131025|archive-date=2013-11-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=HollywoodReporter1>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/guillermo-del-toros-crimson-peak-650845|publisher=Hollywood Reporter|title=Guillermo del Toro's 'Crimson Peak' Gets February 2014 Start Date|first=Etan|last=Vlessing|date=2013-10-25|access-date=2015-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131027110527/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/guillermo-del-toros-crimson-peak-650845|archive-date=2013-10-27|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Perry-Folino|first=Joanna|title=Interview with Jim Beaver: Actor, Friend, Writer and Film Star|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/joanna-perryfolino/interview-with-jim-beaver_b_4751476.html|publisher=Huffington Post|date=2014-02-13|access-date=2015-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219032429/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/joanna-perryfolino/interview-with-jim-beaver_b_4751476.html|archive-date=2014-12-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年4月14日，安大略省的[[京士頓_(安大略省)|京士頓]]也列作為拍攝地點<ref>{{cite news|url=http://kingstonherald.com/entertainment/crimson-peak-kingston-2010313172|work=Kingston Herald|date=2014-04-14|last=Hart|first=Courtney|title=Crimson Peak Filming in Kingston's Market Square|access-date=2016-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306000022/http://kingstonherald.com/entertainment/crimson-peak-kingston-2010313172|archive-date=2016-03-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

